---
const items = [
  { title: "Marketing site", desc: "Static pages, one CMS bind, sitemap-fed." },
  { title: "Internal tool", desc: "Auth, dashboard, table+drawer pattern." },
  { title: "Customer portal", desc: "Account, billing, support tickets." },
  { title: "E-commerce", desc: "Inventory, cart, payments, fulfillment." },
];
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>astro-asteroids demo</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0A0A0A;
        --ink: #C8C8C8;
        --ink-hi: #FAFAFA;
        --blueprint: #4DD0E1;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; }
      body { padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
      h1 { font-size: 4rem; color: var(--ink-hi); letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
      h2 { color: var(--ink-hi); }
      p { line-height: 1.6; }
      .kicker { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; color: var(--blueprint); letter-spacing: 0.32em; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
      ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
      li { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
      .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #2A2A2A; padding: 1.5rem; }
      .card h3 { color: var(--ink-hi); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
      footer { margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #2A2A2A; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="kicker">astro-asteroids · demo</p>
    <h1>Shoot every word.</h1>
    <p>
      This page exists to give the asteroids overlay a target field. Press the
      Konami code (<code>↑↑↓↓←→←→BA</code>) or click the launcher button at
      the bottom. Use arrow keys to rotate and thrust. Space to fire. ESC to
      exit.
    </p>

    <h2>Pillars</h2>
    <p>Four made-up service pillars so the grid has things to blow up.</p>
    <div class="cards">
      {items.map((it) => (
        <div class="card">
          <h3>{it.title}</h3>
          <p>{it.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2>A long paragraph</h2>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod
      tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim
      veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
      commodo consequat.
    </p>
    <p>
      Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum
      dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non
      proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>One item per line</li>
      <li>Each line a separate target</li>
      <li>Shoot them in any order</li>
      <li>Refresh restores</li>
    </ul>

    <footer>
      <span>astro-asteroids · MIT</span>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
